Find length of string using for loop
=>Using while loop
=>Using len() method
=>Using user-defined function



program 1: Find Length of String using for Loop:

print("Enter the String: ")
text = input()
s = 0
for ch in text:
    s = s+1
print("\nLength =", s)

o/p=enter string 
bannysha
output is 8


Method 2 : using while loop

text = input()
s = 0
while text[s:]:
    s= s+1
print("\nLength =", s)


Method 3: using len() method

print("Enter a String: ", end="")
text = input()
textlen = len(text)
print("\nLength =", textlen)



